<h1>Markdown syntax guide</h1>
<p>
    <b>uBlog</b> uses <a rel="nofollow" href="http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/syntax">Markdown</a> for formatting text,
    as specified in <a rel="nofollow" class="external-link" href="http://commonmark.org/">CommonMark</a>. You should use Markdown in blog posts.
    Markdown is a simple way to format text that looks great on any device.
</p>
